                <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span data-i18n="products.qrpass.bullets.0">Venta online con emisión automática de accesos QR.</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span data-i18n="products.qrpass.bullets.1">Validación en segundos desde móvil o tablet.</span></li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span data-i18n="products.qrpass.bullets.2">Ingreso con reconocimiento facial para elevar la seguridad.</span></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-300/40 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="products.qrpass.flow.0">Vende</span>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-300/40 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="products.qrpass.flow.1">Genera QR</span>
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-slate-300/40 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="products.qrpass.flow.2">Valida</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 3 -->
